<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>There is a bug in the example script in <a href="http://framework.zend.com/manual/en/zend.view.scripts.html">http://framework.zend.com/manual/en/â€¦</a>
about how to instanciate Zend_View_Smarty class.
Code error:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
//Example 1. In initView() of initializer.
$view = new Zend_View_Smarty('/path/to/templates');
$viewRenderer =
    new Zend_Controller_Action_HelperBroker::getStaticHelper('ViewRenderer');
</code></pre>

<p>viewRender line must be</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$viewRenderer = Zend_Controller_Action_HelperBroker::getStaticHelper('ViewRenderer');
</code></pre>

<p>because the static method getStaticHelper() is not a constructor.</p>

